<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="opposite-n">opposite <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /'ɒpəzɪt/    美 /'ɑːpəzət/  </p>
<p>[C] [常用the opposite]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>反义词；对立面；对立物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Long is <strong>the opposite of</strong> short.
长是短的反义词。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I didn’t feel sleepy at all — <strong>just the opposite</strong>, in fact.
我一点儿都不困，事实上正好相反。</p></div></div>